data.description: Charming duplex in the heart of downtown Charleston, short walk from MUSC (who needs the parking headache when you can walk to work), Joe Riley Park, shops, restaurants and more. Property has been completely gutted and renovated from its previous condition all the way from the sub flooring to the framing. Each unit has 2 bedrooms/1 bathroom with granite countertops and stainless steel appliances making them very attractive rentals for the downtown market. Both units are currently vacant, prior to homeowner had a waitlist of prospective tenants.
